data.description:
Step into this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow right off the historical Independence square. Inside, you'll discover three cozy bedrooms, an updated kitchen and bathroom, and a yard ready for your personal touch. 
This bungalow's location near the Independence square, which means close to shopping, adds to its appeal. Don't miss this chance to make it your own for less than you can rent. Schedule a viewing today and start living in this character-filled home!
